rawContent:
Every Blanchet House meal service is staffed with two peer support specialists with the Old Town InReach Program (OTIP). Lunch and dinner services are staffed by in-house shelter referral specialist Jennifer Coon. Jennifer refers meal guests to Bybee Lakes Hope Center and TPI shelters every day. Referring requires Jennifer to make multiple phone calls and emails and fill out paperwork for every individual which can take hours and days to get a response. Only yesterday she worked all day to find shelter for a 61-year-old female meal guest. TPI won’t have a bed for her until tomorrow.
You can learn more about the OTIP team at https://t.co/uQNBobtZFk. You can learn more about Jennifer at https://t.co/aDYzgJjrND.
